OL,3,CBritons warned that bird feeders can
OL,4,Cspread avian diseases
OL,6,FThe Royal Society for the Protection
OL,7,Fof Birds (RSPB) has urged people to
OL,8,Fadjust how they use their bird feeders
OL,9,Fto prevent the spread of diseases that
OL,10,Fare lowering numbers of some species.
OL,12,FIt comes after average counts of
OL,13,Fstarlings per garden hit record lows
OL,14,Ffor the second year running,
OL,15,Fdecreasing a further 3% in this year's
OL,16,Fbirdwatch.
OL,18,FThe RSPB said the species has seen an
OL,19,F85.1% decline since the scheme began
OL,20,Fin 1979.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
