CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775823079
OL,3,CBritons warned that bird feeders can
OL,4,Cspread avian diseases
OL,6,FMeanwhile, greenfinches saw the
OL,7,Faverage count rise slightly by 2.3%
OL,8,Fthis year but the charity said the
OL,9,Fnumber is still two-thirds lower than
OL,10,Fin 1979.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
