OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775823079
OL,3,CBritons warned that bird feeders can
OL,4,Cspread avian diseases
OL,6,FRSPB scientists said the songbirds are
OL,7,Famong the species at risk from
OL,8,Fdiseases that can spread at bird
OL,9,Ffeeders and are urging households to
OL,10,Fmake adjustments to when, how and what
OL,11,Ffood they provide.
OL,13,FBeccy Speight, the charity's chief
OL,14,Fexecutive, said they're not asking
OL,15,Fpeople to stop feeding birds, but just
OL,16,Fto ensure they're doing it in a way
OL,17,Fthat protects the birds' health.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
