CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775823079
OL,3,CBritons warned that bird feeders can
OL,4,Cspread avian diseases
OL,6,F"Feeding birds is something millions
OL,7,Fof us love and value but the science
OL,8,Fshows us that birds such as
OL,9,Fgreenfinches have been affected by the
OL,10,Fspread of disease at feeders."
OL,12,FThis year, more than 650,000 people
OL,13,Ftook part in the birdwatch, which
OL,14,Finvolves spending an hour counting
OL,15,Fbirds in a garden or local green space
OL,16,Fduring the last weekend in January.
OL,18,FThe results can help conservationists
OL,19,Fgauge how the country's bird life is
OL,20,Ffaring.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
