OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775823080
OL,3,CBritons warned that bird feeders can
OL,4,Cspread avian diseases
OL,6,FThe charismatic birds are found across
OL,7,Fthe UK, with numbers swelling during
OL,8,Fwinter when more of the species arrive
OL,9,Ffrom northern Europe, and can be seen
OL,10,Fin huge numbers performing aerial
OL,11,Fdisplays known as "murmurations".
OL,13,FBefore the year 2000, starlings were
OL,14,Fregularly the most numerous species
OL,15,Frecorded in the Big Garden Birdwatch.
OL,17,FHowever, they are now "red-listed"
OL,18,Fbecause of concerns over their falling
OL,19,Fpopulation.
OL,26,@sD@SOUsD@`O]yD@WOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775823080
OL,3,CBritons warned that bird feeders can
OL,4,Cspread avian diseases
OL,6,FThe RSPB said there is a lack of
OL,7,Fevidence behind what might be driving
OL,8,Fthe decline although a fall in chicks'
OL,9,Fsurvival rates over their first winter
OL,10,Fcould be contributing.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, greenfinches ` which came
OL,13,Fin 18th place ` have seen their
OL,14,Fpopulation particularly devastated by
OL,15,Fthe disease trichomonosis, which
OL,16,Fspreads more easily when birds gather
OL,17,Faround feeders in summer and autumn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775823080
OL,3,CBritons warned that bird feeders can
OL,4,Cspread avian diseases
OL,6,FThe songbird is also on the
OL,7,Fconservation "red list", with other UK-
OL,8,Fwide surveys indicating a loss of more
OL,9,Fthan two million birds since the mid-
OL,10,F1990s.
OL,12,FThe charity's experts said households
OL,13,Fshould feed birds seasonally,
OL,14,Fadjusting what goes into feeders
OL,15,Fduring the summer and autumn months
OL,16,Fwhen the risk of disease spreading is
OL,17,Fhigher.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@WO]
