OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775823080
OL,3,CBritons warned that bird feeders can
OL,4,Cspread avian diseases
OL,6,FThis could include a pause on seed and
OL,7,Fpeanuts to prevent too many birds
OL,8,Fgathering in one place, although small
OL,9,Famounts of mealworms, fat balls or
OL,10,Fsuet are safe to provide year-round.
OL,12,FOther recommendations include cleaning
OL,13,For moving feeders weekly, changing
OL,14,Fwater daily and retiring flat-surfaced
OL,15,Ffeeders after research found a higher
OL,16,Frisk of disease spread on flat
OL,17,Fsurfaces, including bird tables.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
