OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775823080
OL,3,CBritons warned that bird feeders can
OL,4,Cspread avian diseases
OL,6,FWhen launching the survey in January,
OL,7,Fthe RSPB said bird lovers could enjoy
OL,8,Fa bumper year for migratory species
OL,9,Fafter cold and unsettled weather
OL,10,Facross Europe.
OL,12,FThe results suggested the number of
OL,13,Fredwing and fieldfare recorded did
OL,14,Fsurge this year, with average counts
OL,15,Frising by 307% and 70% respectively.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
